{"tid":2090991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新任入境處長區嘉宏︰國安法是中央對港府愛護及支持","createTime":"2020-07-02T12:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T12:56:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"74541665ee7cec525c3b5acd29a89061b94eb93c","tid":2090991,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"新上任入境處長區嘉宏今午（2日）會見傳媒時表示，對中央任命感榮幸，將繼續帶領入境處，做好作為紀律部隊的執法及服務，以及維護國家安全。區嘉宏又說，香港已落實《港區國安法》，強調國安法是中央政府對港府的愛護及支持，有助一國兩制恆久發展。<br />\n<br />\n被問到落實港區國安法，入境處會如何審查出入境者，區嘉宏表示會按一切適用法律及政策，去處理每宗個案，而每宗個案會就其個別情況作詳細考慮及決定。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，本港過去一年出現暴力事件，已影響民生、經濟及香港的國際形象，期望國安法的實施有助社會穩定，以及提升國際形象，增加投資及營商機會。"},{"pid":"f86aa48433fedec8b4fa3309ac2ee8bd2deec9d5","tid":2090991,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:47:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200702/s00001/1593689212834/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200702%2Fs00001%2F1593689212834%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8OzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=413063d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200702%2Fs00001%2F1593689212834%2F&h=d3dbfba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200702/s00001/1593689212834/</a>"},{"pid":"e1faef5946a4e2bd6716d1cf5d3ed7a6df57616b","tid":2090991,"uid":97398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f86aa48433fedec8b4fa3309ac2ee8bd2deec9d5","tid":2090991,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:47:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200702/s00001/1593689212834/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200702%2Fs00001%2F1593689212834%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8OzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=413063d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200702%2Fs00001%2F1593689212834%2F&h=d3dbfba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200702/s00001/1593689212834/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:56:15.000Z","msg":"咁點解回歸左咁多年先黎立法，處長暗示中央之前就唔愛香港？"},{"pid":"697d03ac20e05748aff29a960b17cfa4486963fa","tid":2090991,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}